resources.string: Credenz is the annual technical symposium organised by the PICT IEEE Student Branch. Inaugurated in 2004, with an aim to celebrate talent, it has prospered to become one of the finest technical events in the country. Credenz not only infuses a competitive spirit among participants, but it also provides an informative edge through various seminars and workshops conducted by eminent industry professionals. Participants get to experience a diversity of events, workshops and seminars on recent technologies.\n\nThe Student branch has always believed in encouraging students to think beyond the academic domain and challenge their potential.
